<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color:#222;">
<p>Hi {{ recipient_email.split('@')[0] }},</p>

<p>
This is {{ full_name }}.  
I came across your profile and thought I’d reach out directly.
</p>

<p>
{{ candidate_intro }}
</p>

<p>
If this isn’t relevant, no worries at all.
</p>

<p>
Best,<br>
<strong>{{ full_name }}</strong><br>
{% if linkedin_url %}<a href="{{ linkedin_url }}">LinkedIn Profile</a><br>{% endif %}
Email: {{ candidate_email }}
</p>

<hr style="border:none; border-top:1px solid #eee; margin:20px 0;">

<p style="font-size:11px; color:#999;">
    To stop receiving these emails, you can <a href="{{ unsubscribe_link }}" style="color:#999;">Unsubscribe</a>
</p>
</body>
</html>
